data.description: Here is a great opportunity to make some sweat equity into this home. Single level home with a small unfinished basement. Property is sold as-is and would make a great flip project for any buyer. There is a detached 2 bay garage and storage areas out back. Large .36 acre lot that is fully fenced. Buyers please contact a Realtor licensed in Oregon to help you with this property.
